milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (165) involving teams England & Pakistan in ODIs
Asif Iqbal has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for PAK, going past Asif Masood
Underwood and Bob Taylor's 40-run partnership is the highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 37 between Dayle Hadlee and Lance Cairns
Underwood and Bob Taylor's 40-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between Alan Knott and Ken Shuttleworth
Mushtaq Mohammad and Zaheer Abbas's 24-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between Asif Iqbal and Zaheer Abbas
